"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Title_260936" = "Who can see your questions?";
"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Tips_260936" = "The account owner, host, and panelists will be able to see who you are, your contact information (if you're logged in or you provided it), and your question — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nIf your question is selected, it will be visible to all attendees.";
"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Tips_731594" = "The account owner, host, and co-host will be able to see who you are, your contact information (if you're logged in or you provided it), and your question — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nIf your question is selected, it will be visible to all participants.";
"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Public_Tips_260936" = "This Q&A is public, so everyone can see your questions.\n\nThe account owner, host, and panelists will be able to see who you are, your contact information (if you're logged in or you provided it), and your question — and can share them with apps and others.";
"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Public_Tips_523719" = "This Q&A is public, so everyone can see your questions.\n\nThe account owner, host, and co-host will be able to see who you are, your contact information (if you're logged in or you provided it), and your question — and can share them with apps and others.";
"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Anonymous_Tips_260936" = "Unless you submit anonymously, the account owner, host, and panelists will be able to see who you are, your contact information (if you're logged in or you provided it), and your question — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nIf your question is selected, it will be visible to all attendees.";
"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Anonymous_Tips_523719" = "Unless you submit anonymously, the account owner, host, and co-host will be able to see who you are, your contact information (if you're logged in or you provided it), and your question — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nIf your question is selected, it will be visible to all participants.";
"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Public_Anonymous_Tips_260936" = "This Q&A is public, so everyone can see your questions.\n\nThe account owner, host, and panelists will be able to see who you are, your contact information (if you're logged in or you provided it), and your question — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nIf you submit your questions anonymously, nobody can see who submitted your questions.";
"LN_QA_Legal_Notice_Public_Anonymous_Tips_523719" = "This Q&A is public, so everyone can see your questions.\n\nThe account owner, host, and co-host will be able to see who you are, your contact information (if you're logged in or you provided it), and your question — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nIf you submit your questions anonymously, nobody can see who submitted your questions.";
"LN_Chat_Legal_Title_260936" = "Who can see your messages?";
"LN_Chat_Legal_Archive_Title_260936" = "Who can see your messages? Archiving on";
"LN_Chat_Legal_Record_Title_260936" = "Who can see your messages? Recording on";
"LN_Chat_Legal_Tips_260936" = "Everyone in the meeting can see and save your messages with everyone — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nOnly you and those you chat with can save your direct messages and share them with apps and others.";
"LN_Chat_Legal_Archive_Tips_260936" = "Archiving is on, so the account owner can see all your messages — including your direct messages — and share them with apps and others.\n\nEveryone in the meeting can save and share the messages you send to everyone.";
"LN_Chat_Legal_Record_Tips_260936" = "Recording is on, so the account owner and everyone in the meeting can see and save messages sent to everyone — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nOnly you and those you chat with can save your direct messages and share them with apps and others.";
"LN_Chat_Legal_PMC_Record_Tips_260936" = "Recording is on, so the account owner and everyone in the meeting can see and save messages sent to meeting group chat — and can share them with apps and others. These messages will also be posted in the dedicated meeting group chat in Team Chat, and everyone there, including those not in the meeting, can see, save and share them.\n\nOnly you and those you chat with can save your direct messages and share them with apps and others.";
"LN_Chat_Legal_Local_Record_Tips_260936" = "Recording is on, so everyone in the meeting can see and save messages sent to everyone — and can share them with apps and others.\n\nOnly you and those you chat with can save your direct messages and share them with apps and others.";
"LN_Chat_Legal_PMC_Local_Record_Tips_260936" = "Recording is on, so everyone in the meeting can see and save messages sent to meeting group chat — and can share them with apps and others. These messages will also be posted in the dedicated meeting group chat in Team Chat, and everyone there, including those not in the meeting, can see, save and share them.\n\nOnly you and those you chat with can save your direct messages and share them with apps and others.";

